plain splice, no incut:
  (((`"` hello)))
single-incut:
  (((`"` `x=` (X))))
incut + suffix:
  (((`"` `x=` (X) `, done`)))
two incuts:
  (((`"` `a=` (A) `, b=` (B))))
incut with expression:
  (((`"` `sum=` ((`+` X Y)))))
method call inside incut:
  (((`"` `sz=` ((`.` Xs n)))))
nested string literal inside incut:
  (((`"` `x=` ((`"` inner)))))
nested incut with text * N (matrix idiom):
  (((`"` (((`*` (`"` `0 `) 10))) `
`)))
